# vlc

[Display]                                                                                                                                                                                                         │
│ h,H                    Show/Hide help box                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ i                      Show/Hide info box                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ M                      Show/Hide metadata box                                                                                                                                                                    │
│ L                      Show/Hide messages box                                                                                                                                                                    │
│ P                      Show/Hide playlist box                                                                                                                                                                    │
│ B                      Show/Hide filebrowser                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ x                      Show/Hide objects box                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ S                      Show/Hide statistics box                                                                                                                                                                  │
│ Esc                    Close Add/Search entry                                                                                                                                                                    │
│ Ctrl-l                 Refresh the screen                                                                                                                                                                        │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                  │
│[Global]                                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ q, Q, Esc              Quit                                                                                                                                                                                      │
│ s                      Stop                                                                                                                                                                                      │
│ <space>                Pause/Play                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ f                      Toggle Fullscreen                                                                                                                                                                         │
│ c                      Cycle through audio tracks                                                                                                                                                                │
│ v                      Cycle through subtitles tracks                                                                                                                                                            │
│ b                      Cycle through video tracks                                                                                                                                                                │
│ n, p                   Next/Previous playlist item                                                                                                                                                               │
│ [, ]                   Next/Previous title                                                                                                                                                                       │
│ <, >                   Next/Previous chapter                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ <left>,<right>         Seek -/+ 1%                                                                                                                                                                               │
│ a, z                   Volume Up/Down                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ m                      Mute                                                                                                                                                                                      │
│ <up>,<down>            Navigate through the box line by line                                                                                                                                                     │
│ <pageup>,<pagedown>    Navigate through the box page by page                                                                                                                                                     │
│ <start>,<end>          Navigate to start/end of box                                                                                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                  │
│[Playlist]                                                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ r                      Toggle Random playing                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ l                      Toggle Loop Playlist                                                                                                                                                                      │
│ R                      Toggle Repeat item                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ o                      Order Playlist by title                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ O                      Reverse order Playlist by title                                                                                                                                                           │
│ g                      Go to the current playing item                                                                                                                                                            │
│ /                      Look for an item                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ ;                      Look for the next item                                                                                                                                                                    │
│ A                      Add an entry                                                                                                                                                                              │
│ D, <backspace>, <del>  Delete an entry                                                                                                                                                                           │
│ e                      Eject (if stopped)                                                                                                                                                                        │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                  │
│[Filebrowser]                                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ <enter>                Add the selected file to the playlist                                                                                                                                                     │
│ <space>                Add the selected directory to the playlist                                                   
│ .                      Show/Hide hidden files                                                                                                                                                                    │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                  │
│[Player]                                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ <up>,<down>            Seek +/-5%                                                                                                                                                                                │


# unused
│ L                      Show/Hide messages box                                                                                                                                                                    │
